        <headline>Special Weather Statement issued August 17 at 3:18PM MDT by NWS Pocatello ID</headline>
        <description>At 318 PM MDT, Doppler radar was tracking a strong thunderstorm near
Almo, or 14 miles southwest of Malta, moving northeast at 5 mph.

HAZARD...Penny size hail.

SOURCE...Radar indicated.

IMPACT...Minor hail damage to outdoor objects is possible.

Locations impacted include...
Elba.
</description>
        <instruction>If outdoors, consider seeking shelter inside a building.</instruction>
